Assembly is the structure that functions to serve "X" job as fast and efficient as possible.
It is good for cheap work that needs to be done fast.
Assembly is less quality for more quantity.
High level languages are more complicated and contain more errors for the reward of high quality/special functions whilst the low level languages are the complete opposite of that.
Java is more along the lines of high level languages because of the simplicity with lack of changes from a computers origin functions.
Assembly is more along the lines of low level programming that doesnt diviate from the computer original function.
